<br>
Belle's mother was an Amazon. Aly did not wish to turn her away. Though Belle was raised in Rome, she was not a Roman. She did not fight with Livia, nor did she join Rome's legions. . . . Aly had done that in her past. <br>
<br>
Belle's actions had always been for the greater good, and in becomming Alysia's daughter, it was her rite to hold the position of Princess.<br>
