&quot;Then give her nothing, Dawn, and she where her loyalties will lie as we all will. But I'm telling you this now. If she is not as bad as we both think, the day she proves this to us, if it happens, what will she think of you? A true Amazon can reveal herself against the harshest terms, and those who were against her will not always receive the warmest welcome... I know that it matters little in your heart, as it is in mine, but still... allies are few, great Queens are fewer, and Every last one is precious.&quot;<br>
